Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.35,0:00:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,且慢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有要物遗忘在此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便当哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.73,0:00:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天放了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.08,0:00:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋包饭的说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.35,0:00:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢…谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也注意别迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.66,0:00:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白的说
