Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.71,0:01:21.40,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我的眼睛 映照出久远的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:24.75,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}选择什么 放弃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:27.96,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我如何能 自行定夺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:31.17,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}选取之物 早已在心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:34.10,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}向神问询 是否有误
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:37.22,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}其实不曾孤独过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:39.77,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}其实一直在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.81,0:01:46.84,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}现在 伸出手去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.98,0:01:50.08,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}已经无所畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.18,0:01:53.59,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}哪怕化身怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:02:01.67,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我一定 会做到
