Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.51,0:02:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到本校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里所有学生都有特殊能力吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大多数学生只是有这种可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是出现了预兆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点兆头就得来这里吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.55,0:02:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从前 我们这种特殊能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.26,0:02:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都会变成脑科学家的小白鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦被抓住 人生就完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵 太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的就是我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某人设立了现在这个系统
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没能保护到哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你还让我加入学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我使用能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生会身负特殊任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要以最快的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找出并保护你这种校外的能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者进行恐吓 让人不再用能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭什么要我干这些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干活是会有辛苦费的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步未妹妹在家自己做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为家里伙食费吃紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…我叫乙坂有宇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前在阳野森高中上学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.09,0:03:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 她才高一就当学生会长了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的学生会长 不管高几都能当
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选人所看重的是能力者的责任感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有行动力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,0)}（可喜可贺）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和昨天的晚饭完全一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙坂同学午饭怎么吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…我什么都没带
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 一起去食堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带你去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不叫上她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不介意的话 就叫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有空位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就买点三明治 回教室吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 柜台前也排长队呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我用能力大显身手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？可以用能力吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 我会在摄像机的死角下活动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我的速度太快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具体会拿到哪种 就得看运气了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:04:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆炸？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 今天的战利品不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是猪排三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也算成功？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都伤成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的校服下面有防具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并没有受太大的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑袋都喷血了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人不可貌相
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙其实相当危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 全是猪排三明治啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用瞬间移动抓的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:06:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得有时间去挑？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且全都压坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用瞬间移动抓的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得有办法调节抓取的力度？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个有缺陷的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她连同性朋友都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是让特定的单个对象看不到她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 对象之外的人都能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她现在的处境
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以说是能力的缺陷所导致的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然她打人都有她的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 当大家看到她在用能力施暴时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心里会怎么想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更何况 摄像头会如实录下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她打架的过程
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久而久之 难免会遭人厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 听说她在上初中前就没这脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 她来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,协助者要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要我们去学生会室集合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？这你都能懂？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底要干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇！什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能力是 念摄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特殊能力者的所在地和能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:07:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是「协助者」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南波高中…搞伏击好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翘课过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是去搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又不是警察
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果警察比我们先找到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个能力者的人生就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始查访
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本就是问问最近有没有出过怪事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的目标是念摄能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以问问和照片有关的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑子有病 谁陪你们玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人形迹可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快用你的能力入侵 去翻他的包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:08:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护特殊能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 要去搞谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 浪费我时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人都找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 我干嘛要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这所学校女生的照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美女呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一张是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…女生的内衣照吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,念摄能力拍的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你拍的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 是买来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:09:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问谁买的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.17,0:10:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事我不会外传
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请如实告知真相
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就把你干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉这照片上的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有动…高二E班
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲啊 去抓住高二E班的有动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有动同学回家了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.66,0:10:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？有动同学啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人？哪冒出来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用念摄能力拍这种下流照片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还拿来卖钱的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是弓道部部长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照片？念摄能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的客人都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 你的柜子也搜过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面那一大堆照片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都用摄像机录下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活动室的柜子 还是很容易弄开的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 做这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为能卖钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经济困难是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠这个赚钱 你父母不会开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们病了！没办法啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经念摄了你的内衣照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸也拍进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手 否则我就四处散播这张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？这么快就念摄完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忒厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这种照片没人看的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么看都是美女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？有人夸我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 所以你快滚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照片…没了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…在你那…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折腾人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被将死了 认输吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你看到的都给我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用弓箭指向别人 真差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的武道精神…吃屎了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.14,0:12:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会把你交给警察的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 如果你继续使用特殊能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的人生就毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想变成科学家的实验品 被解剖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解剖？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我警告你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的能力过了青春期就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要钱 请通过打工来正当赚取
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//----------------------------TXTB----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解决得很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们总是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不再让特殊能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成我哥哥那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问一下 你那被科学家抓住的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来怎样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事也没什么好隐瞒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天去看看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没吃午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就去小卖部买车站便当吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:13.51,note3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(864,985)}Kiosk
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:15.41,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(160,45)}厚片 牛舌便当
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:15.41,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(90,45)}拉线自动加热
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉线自动加热的牛舌便当
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得很厉害对不？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…我本来就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是急行电车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在车里还吃得下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.32,0:14:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,严重违反公德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？你不吃三明治吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先是哥哥 变成了特殊能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我刚考上国立大学附中时的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 我考上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力没有白费啊 奈绪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你以后能当博士或大官呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 你看这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我考上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真考上啦？你真厉害 比我强多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里哪里 哥哥比我厉害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥说过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有唱片公司看上你们乐队了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家里这么穷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.08,0:15:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真想早点出道 独立成人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 之前借你的CD 你听了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没听 会影响学习的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.13,0:15:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考都考完了 你就听听嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想奏出的 就是那种声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对摇滚没什么兴趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 ZHIEND不是摇滚 是后摇滚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前跟我长篇大论过啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么前前后后的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我没能入学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件大事 要和你们说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了进一步发挥你们的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定送你们去一所全寄宿制的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都快和唱片公司签约了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.04,0:16:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,签约…晚点也不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能独立挣钱 对家里也是好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说反了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我的话 才能改善家里的经济状况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫说反了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈绪倒是很会读书
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我是个只会弹吉他的笨蛋啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这项优点被人看中了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 要去的是乐校？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那干嘛要我们都去？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天 我们第一次见到母亲跪了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是多年来 独自把我们养大的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.27,0:16:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去的地方 看起来是所学校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很快就有了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 每天上完课后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要接受一种类似体检的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明同校 我和哥哥却见不了面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每当我想去找哥哥时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友们都会拦住我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那期间 哥哥一直在充当实验品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥的能力 能随意让空气发生振动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在演唱会上使用能力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让吉他发出各种声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并因此被那些人盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用哥哥的能力 可以干扰通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能劫持无线电信号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学家们构想了许多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概过了一年 我才见到哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时 哥哥已不再是从前的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经不认识我这个妹妹了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.31,0:17:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拦在我和哥哥之间的朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:18:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也全都是科学家布置的假朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每天都要接受体检
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为兄妹都是特殊能力者的可能性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在心里发誓 不再相信任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并逃出了那所「学校」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来…怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我遇见了唯一可以信赖的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 下一站下车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是友利奈绪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来见我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她名叫奈绪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在12号房
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能带他去外面吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不出园区就行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇定剂又失效了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人…到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在作曲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥现在 以为自己在弹吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听见的吼叫 就是曲调 是主旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.43,0:19:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 被子又毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去走走好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是风景最好的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很赞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么特别的环境 到底是谁…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了我那唯一可以信赖的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥能免费住进这所最美的医院
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全靠那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人愿意为你们做这么多吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 还是完全没兴趣的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 说不定很快就会有特效药
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人在搞治疗这种患者的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对科学家来说 能力者就像干电池一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.51,0:20:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用完就丢 再换别的能力者来做实验
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成这样的「原能力者」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无拯救的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的我们 也不知会变成什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别吓人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动动脑子再说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:20:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这人 挺不容易的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想同情我？算了吧 你这作弊狂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.39,0:21:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不该是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到学生会的工作这么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？有宇哥哥进学生会了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？我没告诉你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次听你说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就用小步特制蔬菜多多咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化去身心劳顿罢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:39.05,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,咖喱 咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:43.73,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,蔬菜多多 吃咖喱的说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:47.48,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,咖喱咖喱 咕噜咕噜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然我是能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么步未也有变成能力者的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我被抓走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.69,0:21:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 步未也会像友利一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.44,0:21:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开吃喽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.07,0:21:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好甜！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.26,0:21:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这…这咖喱里面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.45,0:21:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放的调味料是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙坂家秘传披萨酱是也！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}（乙坂家 秘传！披萨酱）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.77,0:22:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这吃起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.02,0:22:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟蛋包饭一模一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.88,0:22:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你每天都看也行 但要早点睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.82,0:22:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天看到了彗星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太激动了 我会边兴奋边睡觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.62,0:22:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也能睡得着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.55,0:22:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真正想看的 其实是另一颗彗星的说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.51,0:22:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是颗长周期彗星的说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.43,0:22:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.44,0:22:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃是数百年方能一遇之彗星！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.93,0:22:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这种彗星啊
