Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.31,0:23:08.90,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}待有强风吹过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:14.76,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,250)}吹走心中迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.07,0:23:18.71,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}世界尽头的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.75,0:23:22.34,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我们竟不知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.44,0:23:26.03,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}生命中的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.15,0:23:29.72,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}竟也无法摈弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.82,0:23:33.37,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}继续向前走去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.49,0:23:37.14,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}终能寻获勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.24,0:23:40.71,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}梦却向我预示
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.85,0:23:44.50,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}寻获既是结束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.58,0:23:48.21,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}天空改貌换颜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.27,0:23:51.93,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}群星流转不息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.99,0:23:55.61,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}待到梦醒之后
